object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct insured.SystemId,
                insured.ParentId,
                insured.CMMContainer,
                insured.Id,
                insured.IndexName,
                insured.StatusCd,
                insured.EntityTypeCd,
                insured.PreferredDeliveryMethod,
                insured.TemporaryAddressOverrideInd,
                insured.NoEmailInd,
                insured.InspectionContact,
                insured.InspectionContactNumber,
                insured.InspectionContactPhoneType,
                insured.RowId
FROM insured
where insured.cmmcontainer = 'Policy'
  and insured.systemid in (select systemid
                           from advrxxchangedbeans
                           where concat(adddt, addtm) >= '2023-10-20 00:00:00.000'
                             and concat(adddt, addtm) <= '2023-12-12 00:00:00.000'
                             and cmmcontainer = 'Policy')

SELECT distinct basicpolicy.SystemId,
                basicpolicy.PolicyNumber,
                basicpolicy.InceptionDt,
                BasicPolicy.PolicyVersion as PolicyVersion
FROM basicpolicy
where basicpolicy.cmmcontainer = 'Policy'
  and basicpolicy.systemid in (select systemid
                               from advrxxchangedbeans
                               where concat(adddt, addtm) >= '2023-10-20 00:00:00.000'
                                 and adddt <= '2023-12-12 00:00:00.000'
                                 and cmmcontainer = 'Policy')
